@rocofoucault @sbagen I couldn't have said it better, Roco.

He's absolutely awful, but crafty so we have to keep an eye on him. Whenever I see him, I am put in mind of @DrIbram X. Kendi's chapter on Black racists in his book "How To Be An Antiracist."

My Black West Point grad veteran husband agrees. https://t.co/M6sxHZy8j2
